'''聖瓦倫丁'''，[[天主教會|天主教會]] 譯為'''羅馬的聖華楞定'''（{{lang-la|Valentinus}}）是一位廣受尊崇的三世紀羅馬[[基督教聖人|聖人]]，紀念日在2月14日，自[[中世紀中期|中世紀中期]]起便和[[宮廷愛情|宮廷愛情]]有連繫。除了名字和2月14日死在[[弗拉米尼亞大道|弗拉米尼亞大道]]，他的其他事跡並沒有可靠記載。不肯定聖瓦倫丁是一位聖人還是兩位同名的聖人。後期的[[聖人傳記|聖人傳記]]加入了一些不同的故事。因此，他的紀念日不被保留在1969年修訂的[[天主教聖人曆|天主教聖人曆]]，但他仍在2月14日在特別羅馬聖人曆受尊崇。<ref>''Calendarium Romanum'' Libreria Editrice Vaticana (1969), p. 117</ref>可是，「2月14日在羅馬[[米爾維奧橋|米爾維奧橋]]附近弗拉米尼亞大道殉難的殉道者瓦倫丁」仍在官方認可給各地景仰的聖人表中。<ref>''"Die 14 februarii memoria Romae via Flaminia iuxta pontem Milvium, sancti Valentini, martyris"''. See ''[[Martyrologium_Romanum|Martyrologium Romanum]]'', Libreria Editrice Vaticana, 2001, p. 141 (February 14).</ref>

今日，[[聖瓦倫丁節|聖瓦倫丁節]]是[[普世聖公宗|普世聖公宗]]和[[信義宗|信義宗]]的正式慶日。<ref name=Anglican>{{cite web|url=http://www.churchofengland.org/prayer-worship/worship/texts/the-calendar/holydays.aspx|title=Holy Days|year=2012|publisher=[[Church_of_England|Church of England]] (Anglican Communion)|accessdate=October 27, 2012|quote=February 14 Valentine, Martyr at Rome, c.269|archive-date=2018-12-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181225084824/https://www.churchofengland.org/prayer-and-worship/join-us-daily-prayer|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Pfatteicher2008">{{cite book|last=Pfatteicher|first=Philip H.|title=New Book of Festivals and Commemorations: A Proposed Common Calendar of Saints|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=W82FOCZ4hmwC&pg=PA86|accessdate=October 27, 2012|date=August 1, 2008|publisher=Fortress Press|isbn=9780800621285|page=86|quote=IO February 14 The Lutheran Service Book, with its penchant for the old Roman calendar, commemorates Valentine on this date.}}</ref>在[[正教會|正教會]]，聖瓦倫丁監督節在7月6日紀念，而殉道者聖瓦倫丁節在7月30日。<ref>[http://ocafs.oca.org/FeastSaintsLife.asp?FSID=101926 ''Martyr Valentinus the Presbyter and those with him at Rome'']. [[Orthodox_Church_in_America|Orthodox Church in America]] website.</ref> <ref>[http://ocafs.oca.org/FeastSaintsLife.asp?FSID=102148 ''Hieromartyr Valentine the Bishop of Interamna, [[Terni|Terni]] in [[Italy|Italy]]'']. [[Orthodox_Church_in_America|Orthodox Church in America]]</ref>在[[希臘正教會|希臘正教會]]，名為華倫提奴（男）或華倫提娜（女）的信眾可以在西方的教會曆中的2月14日慶祝。<ref>[http://www.eortologio.gr/data/eortes/namedays_february.php Greek Orthodox names in February]</ref>

==圣瓦伦丁钥匙==
圣瓦伦丁也是[[癫痫|癫痫]]的守护者，癫痫曾一度被称作圣瓦伦丁病<ref name="Illes2011">{{cite book|last=Illes|first=Judika|title=Encyclopedia of Mystics, Saints & Sages|accessdate=20 June 2014|date=11 October 2011|publisher=HarperCollins|isbn=978-0-06-209854-2|page=1238|quote=Saint Valentine is invoked for healing as well as love. He protects against fainting and is requested to heal epilepsy and other seizure disorders. In northern Italy, epilepsy was once traditionally known as Saint Valentine's Malady.}}</ref>。圣瓦伦丁钥匙是金属钥匙，可以作为情人间打开心锁的象征，也可以作为驱除癫痫的护身符。直到现在，在意大利[[帕多瓦省|帕多瓦省]][[蒙塞利切|蒙塞利切]]的一个小教堂，圣-{zh-hans:乔; zh-hk:喬;}-治堂，每年2月14日都会举行一个特别仪式，儿童们会得到一个小的金钥匙来避开癫痫<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://web.prm.ox.ac.uk/amulets/index.php/keys-amulet2/index.html |title=Pitt Rivers Museum, Oxford, "St Valentine Key, Italy" |accessdate=2015-02-19 |archive-date=2014-07-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140719150116/http://web.prm.ox.ac.uk/amulets/index.php/keys-amulet2/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
